	<description>
鼠异的诅咒机制非常有趣，但是不能只对殖民者生效，本模组对鼠异诅咒补丁打了补丁，并增加了模组选项，只对殖民者生效。

The RACurse is really interesting, but it cannot be configured to affect only colonists. This mod adds configurable options to limit its effects to colonists only.
	</description>
